title: No images are shown
body:
I tried all possible options and also various image sources. However, there is always the same single image shown which says "Sorry, Sorry Retry ..." instead of giving a time. Any idea what's going wrong?

I am on Sony Xperia Z3 Compact with CyanogenMod 12.1 (Android-Version 5.1.1).

title: Image resolution is too low
body:
Hi, thanks a lot for your app, I like it a lot.

Would it be possible to fetch images with a better resolution? My phone has an HD screen, and they look blurred because of the low resolution.
